lement_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d5f0ca5 h2-title-on-light-bg elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"d5f0ca5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">CGB has a strong academic core<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4af5db8 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"4af5db8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a718601 parrafo-pagina-interna elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a718601\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Students in Nursery and Reception follow the VESS curriculum, The International Primary Curriculum (IPC) is taught from Year 1 through Year 6; students in Key Stage 3 follow the International Middle Years Curriculum (IMYC) in Years 7 to 9, all students in Key Stage 4 sit the International General Certificate of Secondary Education (IGCSE) examinations from the University of Cambridge; and the International Baccalaureate Diploma Programme is compulsory for all students in Y12 and Y13.<\/p><p>Throughout the school, the curriculum is delivered in English as a medium of instruction by qualified teachers whose first language is English. Instruction is student-centred and differentiated, and the most up-to-date, research based teaching methodologies are used. Visible Thinking routines are developed within the Primary Section to encourage a culture of thinking and learning from an early age and become active learners within their classrooms. Assessment for learning and collaboration within the classrooms across the whole school are two examples of how we put students in the \u201cdriving seat\u201d.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-479f1f5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"479f1f5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"has_ae_slider elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-95f5563 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-full_width elementor-section-content-middle elementor-section-height-min-height elementor-section-items-stretch elementor-section-height-default ae-bg-gallery-type-default\" data-id=\"95f5563\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;,&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"has_ae_slider elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-fd8e57c animated-fast ae-bg-gallery-type-default elementor-invisible\" data-id=\"fd8e57c\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;,&quot;animation&quot;:&quot;slideInRight&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-699096c elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"699096c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1a5644c h2-title-on-light-bg elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"1a5644c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">CGB was the first school in Colombia to receive a double international accreditation<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0f1466f elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"0f1466f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-13d276f parrafo-pagina-interna elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"13d276f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>From the Council of International Schools (CIS) and the New England Association of Schools and Colleges (NEASC) from the United States.<\/p><p>Ninety five per cent of the classrooms have interactive white boards. The three ICT classrooms, mobile laptop rooms and classroom iPads sets encourage the use of technology as a learning tool and develop digital competencies.<\/p><p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.cgb.edu.co\/outstanding-cambridge-learner-awards\/\">Our IGCSE results improve every year<\/a> and enable our students to be better equipped to face the challenges of studying the IB Diploma Programme, and the IB Diploma pass rate is above the world average. All of our students go on to tertiary education around the world and attend some of the most prestigious universities \u2013 many with scholarships. Nationally, the \u201cPrueba Saber 11\u201d (ICFES) exam results are consistently in the \u201cMuy Superior\u201d category.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"has_ae_slider elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-490c232 animated-fast ae-bg-gallery-type-default elementor-invisible\" data-id=\"490c232\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{&quot;animation&quot;:&quot;slideInLeft&quot;,&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-739c65e elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"739c65e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Strong Academic Core CGB has a strong academic core Students in Nursery and Reception follow the VESS curriculum, The International Primary Curriculum (IPC) is taught from Year 1 through Year 6; students in Key Stage 3 follow the International Middle Years Curriculum (IMYC) in Years 7 to 9, all students in Key Stage 4 sit [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":5,"featured_media":0